 1. PREREQUISITES — Install these first
===========================================================================

--- mpv player (official CI build, NOT mpv.net) ---
  winget install "mpv-player.mpv-CI.MSVC"
This installs mpv.com + mpv.exe (v0.41.0+). Not mpv.net (which exposes mpvnet.exe).

--- Node.js (LTS) ---
  winget install OpenJS.NodeJS.LTS
Or from: https://nodejs.org/

--- aria2c (fast C++ downloader, fallback engine) ---
  winget install aria2.aria2
Or: choco install aria2

--- Global npm packages ---
  npm install -g peerflix

--- Local npm dependencies ---
  cd D:\scripts
  npm install                   (uses package.json, pinned to webtorrent@1.9.4)

Note: Version is pinned to 1.9.4 because webtorrent 2.x+ dropped
File.createServer() which the streaming engine relies on.

